intro_lines = ["Back so soon? Good — got another quick one for you. Bluewater Drive, just four houses. Shouldn't take you long.", "One thing to know: mail in this part of town comes in rough shape. Names worn off, the odd letter smudged. Comes with the territory.", "Use your head, match what you've got. Off you go — good luck!"]
